	<div class="row">
	  <div class="col l6 s12">
		<h5 class="white-text">Wyvern</h5>
		<p class="grey-text text-lighten-4">Wyvern is ment to not have you sign in, so that means it does not collect your data, or any data about anything! There will be private rooms, and public rooms. Public rooms are shown on the main page. Private rooms need a link.</p>
	  </div>
